    <entry>
      <title>Hexo搭建自己的博客笔记</title>
      <link href="/2023-09-28-Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0.html"/>
      <url>/2023-09-28-Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Hexo部署"><a href="#Hexo部署" class="headerlink" title="Hexo部署"></a>Hexo部署</h2><p>根据<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs">Hexo官方文档</a>,需要安装<a href="https://nodejs.org"node.js"/">Node.js</a>(且版本不能低于10.13),还有<a href="https://git-scm.com"git"/">Git</a>。</p><h2 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h2><p>可以使用npm安装,终端输入</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-g</span> hexo-cli<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>或者</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>安装以后可以使用以下两种方式执行Hexo:</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">npx hexo <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>command<span class="token operator">></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>或者添加如下环境变量，可以直接使用Hexo <command>:</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token builtin class-name">echo</span> <span class="token string">'PATH="$PATH:./node_modules/.bin"'</span> <span class="token operator">>></span> ~/.profile<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="搭建博客基本框架"><a href="#搭建博客基本框架" class="headerlink" title="搭建博客基本框架"></a>搭建博客基本框架</h2><p>执行以下命令</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo init <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>folder<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token builtin class-name">cd</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>folder<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>其中<folder>为博客框架放置的位置，可以放置在一个文件夹内，如果没有指定<folder>,则会在当前目录下载框架<br>举个例子，放置在家目录的myblog文件夹中</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo init <span class="token environment constant">$HOME</span>/myblog<span class="token builtin class-name">cd</span> <span class="token environment constant">$HOME</span>/myblog<span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>如果提示权限不足，使用sudo</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">sudo</span> hexo init <span class="token variable">$HONE</span>/myblog<span class="token builtin class-name">cd</span> <span class="token environment constant">$HOME</span>/myblog<span class="token function">sudo</span> <span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="配置HEXO"><a href="#配置HEXO" class="headerlink" title="配置HEXO"></a>配置HEXO</h2><p>在框架所在目录（如上$HOME&#x2F;myblog）中的&#x3D;&#x3D;_config.yml&#x3D;&#x3D;, 为Hexo的配置文件，使用编辑器编辑，详情见<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/configuration">Hexo官方文档</a></p><p>如果你也使用github作为博客部署的仓库，则需要修改如下配置</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none"># URL## Set your site url here. For example, if you use GitHub Page, set url as &#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;username.github.io&#x2F;project&#39;url: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;&lt;yourname&gt;.github.iopermalink: :year&#x2F;:month&#x2F;:day&#x2F;:title&#x2F;permalink_defaults:pretty_urls:  trailing_index: true # Set to false to remove trailing &#39;index.html&#39; from permalinks  trailing_html: true # Set to false to remove trailing &#39;.html&#39; from permalinks<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>将<yourname>修改为你的github用户名</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">deploy:  type: git  repo: &lt;repository url&gt; #https:&#x2F;&#x2F;bitbucket.org&#x2F;JohnSmith&#x2F;johnsmith.bitbucket.io  branch: [branch]<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>将repo修改为仓库所在链接<br>将branch修改为仓库的主分支master（某些时候为main，打开自己的仓库查看）</p><p>安装hexo-deployer-git</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>这时可以尝试生成站点文件推送至远程库，执行</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo generate &amp;&amp; hexo deploy<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>提示输入用户名与密码，用户名为github用户名，密码为github的令牌（某个版本之后不支持密码提交推送）</p><p>提交完成后可以在&#x3D;&#x3D;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;<yourname>.github.io&#x3D;&#x3D;,查看当前博客页面</p><h2 id="Hexo-server"><a href="#Hexo-server" class="headerlink" title="Hexo server"></a>Hexo server</h2><p>提交更改至github需要谨慎，所以半成品可以使用hexo-server在本地查看博客</p><h3 id="安装hexo-server"><a href="#安装hexo-server" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo-server"></a>安装hexo-server</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-server <span class="token parameter variable">--save</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="启动hexo-server"><a href="#启动hexo-server" class="headerlink" title="启动hexo-server"></a>启动hexo-server</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo server<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>根据提示在<a href="http://localhost:4000（或http://127.0.0.1:4000)，查看制作好的页面">http://localhost:4000（或http://127.0.0.1:4000)，查看制作好的页面</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
